<view class="page-container">
  <view class="logo-section">
    <view class="logo">🍼</view>
    <text class="app-name">宝宝成长记</text>
    <text class="app-version">v{{version}}</text>
    <text class="app-slogan">AI智能育儿，科学陪伴成长</text>
  </view>

  <view class="features-card card">
    <view class="card-title">核心功能</view>
    <view class="feature-list">
      <view class="feature-item" wx:for="{{features}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="feature-icon {{item.icon === 'AI' ? 'ai-icon' : ''}}">{{item.icon}}</view>
        <view class="feature-text">
          <text class="feature-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="feature-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="info-card card">
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="info-label">产品理念</text>
      <text class="info-value">宝宝的成长不可逆，每一个功能设计都基于真实的用户需求。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="info-label">数据安全</text>
      <text class="info-value">所有数据加密存储，严格遵循隐私保护法规。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="info-label">联系我们</text>
      <text class="info-value">如有建议或问题，欢迎通过"意见反馈"联系我们。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="copyright">
    <text>© 2026 宝宝成长记</text>
  </view>
</view>
